I am taking PTO to go around Akiba with Faf-kun!
Thank you for all your hard work.
I cannot tell if you are mad or thankful from that response.
Of course this would be a dull competition.
It does not matter if I win or lose,
the work gets done either way.
Want to go to the usual ramen shop?
I will finish this in the meantime.
Beating a mere human like me will not make you very happy, right?
If I made you mad, I will apologize.
And do not sell yourself short.
Do not become a pillar, either.
I have watched many humans become pillars in the other world.
They support others by becoming a sacrifice.
The dragons of the harmony faction help humans,
but many of my companions claimed sacrifices in exchange.
Those people became human pillars and died...
I could not stand watching that.
This discussion's taken an awfully heavy turn.
So, I wish you would stop sacrificing yourself and working so much!
I will lead the others for you!
Miss Kobayashi, you already have Tohru.
Well, if you want that from me, I am willing...
That is called an unnecessary concern.
The world you live in now is not the same as the one you came from.
So, do not go thinking everything is the same.
There are no human sacrifices in modern Japan.
Also, I still have my honor as your senior here, so do not steal my work.
Let us call an end to this competition, okay?
I am glad you were concerned for me.
I am taking you out for drinks with us today.
Takiya-kun's already standing by at our usual place.
I bet it will be fun to drink with everyone.
There are some things you can only talk about when liquored up, too.
And what is with that outfit?!
You dragons piss me off, always dressing like you can do anything!
I think this idea that you can just wear glasses is thoughtless!
As a fellow glasses wearer, there are big differences in size and frames!
If you are going to wear them, I wish you would think about those things first!
This is a popular collaboration cafe!
We are lucky it is emptier on weekdays.
Here is the special bonus illustrated coaster you ordered.
There are 15 types, handed out at random.
You are in this with me until I collect them all!
Lately we have received several reports of a suspicious individual.
They are recruiting people for patrols.
They were hopeful after the skill
I showed catching that thief in the shopping district a while back.
It is unusual to see you in casual clothes.
Miss Kobayashi said I should wear some from time to time.
So, what should I be doing?
Just walk around the area and see if you spot anything strange.
It is a little scary, though.
There is nothing that scares me.
Miss Sasakibe, do you know any martial arts?
You will be a hindrance if anything does happen, then.
They are blocking the street and getting in the way, right?
You are being a nuisance if you loiter there!
You got a problem with us?
Are you some species that cannot understand language?
I will only warn you one more time, so if you cannot understand,
We will make you regret picking a fight with Team Dragon Busters!
Now that is an irritating team name.
Well, let us refocus and get back to our patrol.
What will you do if they come back for revenge?
You are skipping work, are not you?!
I am on patrol to maintain the peace.
You are doing something to preserve the peace of the city?
I just said I am, did not I?!
You have finally found it for yourself?!
From today on you can be an agent of harmony, too!
Allow me to help you with the patrol!
I think she is misunderstanding something again.
Oh, would you like to take my place, then?
You said I would be a hindrance, remember?
I am a bit more experienced at detecting evil.
I would like to know how I can get rid of you.
It is nothing to be embarrassed about.
You can be cute sometimes, too.
Besides, what do you consider evil, anyway?
I will overlook a bit of misconduct as long as it is not bothering others.
There was a book of laws, right?
If they do anything against those, we need to warn them.
It is going to turn red!
That is a clear traffic violation!

Enforcement Order For The Road Traffic Act Article 2 Flashing Blue Light With Person Shaped Symbol Pedestrians shall not begin crossing the road, and pedestrians currently crossing the road must either quickly finish crossing or cease crossing and return to their starting side.
You could be fined up to 20,000 yen!
What are you doing to kids?
You really are a chaos dragon!
If you are going to go after all those little things, I am going home.
And what was that about punishment?
Violence is way worse, you know?
Tohru, you are starting to resemble Miss Kobayashi, are not you?
Elma, you get it, do not you!
You keep focusing on the little things because you are walking without purpose.
Let us search for the suspicious person.
According to the flier, the suspicious person was dressed entirely in black with long hair.
Apparently he is also a tall man with sharp eyes and glasses.
Oh, that is pretty easy to understand.
They said he was spotted dancing on the route to the elementary school.
What is the meaning of this?
I was practicing the choreography for an event with Takiya.
You are a fearsome dragon, so please show more prudence.
A chaos faction member and a harmony faction member happily together...
It would seem this world causes us to go crazy.
And you are the one who is gone the craziest from it.
Are you going to lecture me about being too influenced by it again?
Lately I kind of understand, but...
I still think it is dangerous.
The common sense of this world
does not completely mesh with our understanding,
But is not reconciling that kind of fun?
You did us real good earlier, huh?
Looks like you are pretty capable,
but this time that guy's here.
If you can fight, gender does not matter.
But if you cannot fight, hurry up and apologize.
I will not show any mercy, then.
I will get the clothes Miss Kobayashi gave me dirty.
I told you, did not I?
If you cannot understand, give up hope.
I will make sure you can never oppose me again.
You are getting a lot of greetings today.
Ryuu-san, let us go home already.
I will not just quietly stay defeated!
I will get stronger and have my revenge!
I will show you I have gotten stronger!
When in Rome, Do as the Romans Do (It is Hard to Match Others)
Take, take, take me away somewhere,
jump, jump, jump to Parkour Land!
I want to go to an amusement park!
I never did understand what was so fun about amusement parks.
Have you never been to one, Miss Kobayashi?
If so, we can go and tell you what it is like.
A dragon's going to teach me something about this world?
I will take you to one, since I know them so well!
It is hard to believe we are still in the same country.
So this is the kind of place it is.
The fact that you encounter things you can only find here creates memories,
and the things you interact with let you forget your daily life.
Yes, I am your guide to this world of dreams.
This too could be considered a type of a parlor maid.
Is not that too broad an interpretation?
My father's acquaintance runs this park, so I am helping him out.
Oh, right, there is a cafe I think you would like here in this area.
Kobayashi, I am going to go play with Saikawa and the others.
Meet back up at the Ferris wheel at four.
It is just the two of us adults now, is not it?
Why are you readying a security buzzer?
Wow, a room lined with mirrors, huh?
There are so many reflections of me.
What do they have all these mirrors here for?
I have to accept that I am in human form right now.
I have to say, you are progressing rather quickly, Tohru.
I can generally tell the way from the echoes of sound.
You mean humans try to experience a stronger rotational force
to make themselves aware that they are under the sway of the planet's rotation?
Centrifugal force and rotational force are not
No, let us go with that!
Can I try spinning it, too?
How do you play with it?
This, too, is a maid's duty.
Would he love me, too, then?
Your virginity is mine, so he cannot have it.
I can do it when it counts!
You sure complained quite a bit, though.
As long as I am with you,
even the depths of the abyss where light never reaches would be fun!
I would not have fun there.
Though, I suppose you are right about it being fun because we are together.
You had fun, too, did not you, Miss Kobayashi?
The cafe Georgie-san mentioned should be around here.
That is the Victorian style you mentioned once before.
The best smile she is had at any place we went today?!
Who to drink it with, huh?
You will drink it with me, right?
I am just a little too happy.
You young ladies look like you are having fun.
I took very nice photos of you all.
Shall we all ride the Ferris wheel, then?
We all screamed and had fun.
I would love to live in a place this fun.
Sorry that my place is ordinary and boring.
Nothing, I have just been thinking.
These rides make very sharp turns and rock up and down.
Then there is the buildings with detailed designs
and mascot costumes modeled after fantastical beasts.
is a facility to simulate riding a dragon, is not it?!
I cannot believe they would make these things just because they cannot ride dragons themselves.
How did you even jump to that interpretation?!
In other words, if you rode me you could experience an amusement park every day!
Still, something like this every now and then is not so bad.
It is bad for my hips, though.
You have forgotten your own name, have not you?
I brought the photos from the amusement park.
Let us select the best, then.
I got it, I am sorry.
